ygData.messageBody:
My name is Caniin and I am a monk who lives in Qeynos. I have recently
begun recruiting for a Monk guild based in Qeynos. It's name is The Knights
of the Monastic Brotherhood if you are a monk of level 3 or above please
check out the website: http://kmb.freeservers.com you will find some
information about joining the guild and helping us get started. AS of NOW
we only need 2 more people. So, if you want to be in a new and exciting
guild please check out the above website.................

thanx,
